CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, August 4, 1945 reads: "Play Time! Charming Rosemary Lawrence, Schenley High School graduate, is enjoying a game of shuffleboard at Ammon Pool. - Harris Photo."
TitMainTitle: Portrait of Rosemary Lawrence, wearing two piece floral bathing suit with rick rack trim, kneeling on shuffleboard court at Ammon Pool
